CPRDCY6xSeaMRBMZhdu8W-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bCPRDCY6xSeaMRBMZhdu8W-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bCPRDCY6xSeaMRBMZhdu8W-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bCPRDCY6xSeaMRBMZhdu8W-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bCPRDCY6xSeaMRBMZhdu8W-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bCPRDCY6xSeaMRBMZhdu8W-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bCPRDCY6xSeaMRBMZhdu8W-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bCPRDCY6xSeaMRBMZhdu8W-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bCPRDCY6xSeaMRBMZhdu8W.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bCPRDCY6xSeaMRBMZhdu8W.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSecret Linen Store\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCora Wide Stripe Linen Frill Cushion Covers\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eBold stripes are softened by relaxed linen and frilled edges for a contemporary twist on the ruffle trend.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#39;Dating back to the 16\u003csup\u003eth\u003c/sup\u003e Century, ruffles truly flourished during the Rococo period,\u0026#39; says Georgia at French Bedroom, a time when \u0026#39;fashion embraced femininity, opulence and intricate detailing. The aristocracy, particularly in France, favoured lavish ruffled gowns, lace-trimmed sleeves, and decorative flourishes that exuded elegance and refinement.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#39;The current comeback of ruffles in the home is driven by a desire for both nostalgia and modern romanticism. In the bedroom they lend softness, warmth and whimsy.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"section-how-to-style\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHow to style\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eInterior stylists Laurie Davidson and Réli Farjon of the \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/stylemakerstv/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-url=\"https://www.instagram.com/stylemakerstv/\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"none\"\u003eStyle Makers\u003c/a\u003e say that the best way to style frilled bedding is to embrace the French romanticism to the full. \u0026#39;The ruffled bedding trend is a very pretty and feminine look, so we would style in a French style with accents of pastels and lots of florals,\u0026#39; shares Réli.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-bvyaHv33nxNcTrKNNtUDt5\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=23593\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=idealhome-gb-4907942243772733366\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Ffurn.com%2Fproducts%2Fclaudia-floral-ruffle-duvet-cover-set-multi%3Fsrsltid%3DAfmBOoqT9YmuHTd7MBrUr3Nce8JPvRR34Cu4l_xunT3pFEV9LZhasbTZ\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-url=\"https://furn.com/products/claudia-floral-ruffle-duvet-cover-set-multi?srsltid=AfmBOoqT9YmuHTd7MBrUr3Nce8JPvRR34Cu4l_xunT3pFEV9LZhasbTZ\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=23593\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=hawk-custom-tracking\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Ffurn.com%2Fproducts%2Fclaudia-floral-ruffle-duvet-cover-set-multi%3Fsrsltid%3DAfmBOoqT9YmuHTd7MBrUr3Nce8JPvRR34Cu4l_xunT3pFEV9LZhasbTZ\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"Furn UK\" data-merchant-id=\"205173\" data-merchant-network=\"AW\" data-mer